reviewText: I love the golden era of professional wrestling and this is a great collection of golden era wrestling. You will not see a bunch of high spots and theatrical moves that don't make sence in a competitive display of wrestling infact you will see more traditional theatrical pro wrestling. Hold for hold. This is one of my favorates to study.
A great Collection of classic wrestling. Covers must of the main stars of the ERA. Caution these guys actually know something about wrestling. Bobo Brazil really shines!!!!  GREAT QUALITY !!!!
